        A device which is connected to the Spotify user

        Parameters:
        isActive - If this device is the currently active device.
        isPrivateSession - If this device is currently in a private session.
        isRestricted - Whether controlling this device is restricted. At presentif this is “true” then no Web API commands will be accepted by this device.
        name - The name of the device.
        type - Device type, such as “Computer”, “Smartphone” or “Speaker”.
